<p>A Small Family Business<ref class="image" href="/wiki/File:A_small_family_business.jpg"></ref>Written by<ref target="/wiki/Alan_Ayckbourn" title="Alan Ayckbourn">Alan Ayckbourn</ref>CharactersKen Desmond Harriet Jack Poppy Cliff Anita Samantha Tina Roy Yvonne Benedict The Rivetti BrothersDate premiered21 May 1987Place premiered<ref target="/wiki/England" title="England">England</ref>Original language<ref class="mw-redirect" href="/wiki/English_(language)" title="English (language)">English</ref>SubjectGreed, corruptionGenreDrama<ref class="external text" href="http://womaninmind.alanayckbourn.net/index.htm" rel="nofollow">Official site</ref><ref target="/wiki/Alan_Ayckbourn" title="Alan Ayckbourn">Ayckbourn</ref> chronology</p>
